{"tid":2439191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先出街食lunch比班10後笑","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T04:56:45.000Z","uid":261505,"like":14,"dislike":186,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f54b659e9ed35c926cba93297c11fa512792a4fd","tid":2439191,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n上連登上得多既我見好似個個都話唔裝安心出行<br />\n咁我又跟大隊淨係寫名落紙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔左一排到今日出去食黃店，一開始已經發現唔對路，全部入去既客不論男女老幼都拎手機出黎掃安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心諗幻覺黎既姐，嚇我唔到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就膽粗粗行去問門口店員拎紙仔寫資料，就係呢個時候隔離有班出黎食lunch既10後小學生唔知有心定無意係度大聲笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話呢個人係咪原始人大猩猩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲走埋黎問我係唔係唔識用手機。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻紅都面晒，同店員講我都係轉外賣，跑返公司即刻down返個安心出行再嬲住出呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉 而家d 10後無d禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地80後有素質錢多多聲"},{"pid":"2b0650fd17010dc6717bdffd89b7628f6469b072","tid":2439191,"uid":311626,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"f54b659e9ed35c926cba93297c11fa512792a4fd","tid":2439191,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n上連登上得多既我見好似個個都話唔裝安心出行<br />\n咁我又跟大隊淨係寫名落紙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔左一排到今日出去食黃店，一開始已經發現唔對路，全部入去既客不論男女老幼都拎手機出黎掃安心出行<img src=\"